<HEAD>

<TITLE>RULE 1135.1 - Controlling Emissions of Oxides of Nitrogen from Electric Power Generating Equipment</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
(Adopted by the California Air Resources Board May 27, 1980)
<P>
(Rescinded March 10, 1982)
<P>
<B>RULE 1135.1. CONTROLLING EMISSIONS OF OXIDES OF NITROGEN FROM
ELECTRIC POWER GENERATING EQUIPMENT</B>
<P>
Rescinded on March 10, 1982 by Order of Superior Court Case No.
C 323997.
</BODY>

</HTML>
<P>

</DOC>
