<BODY>

<P>
(Adopted October 5, 1979)(Amended September 10, 1982)<BR>
(Amended April 6, 1984)(Amended July 12, 1985)(Rescinded June
28, 1990)
<P>
<B>RULE 1305. SPECIAL PERMIT PROVISIONS</B>
<P>
Rescinded by the South Coast Air Quality Management District Board
on <BR>
June 28, 1990.
</BODY>

