data records reported for the facility      Data Records  (excluding
the 1F and the 1FT data records).  Right justify and zero fill.
<HR>

<P>
<B>Code 1T - Final Total Record</B>
<P>
The Code 1T data record is used to identify the end of the data
file and must be the last data record reported.<HR>

<P>
Location Field Length Description<HR>
<HR>

<P>
1-4 Record Identifier 4 Constant &quot;1T&quot; followed by 2
blanks<HR>

<P>
5-11 Number of Data  7 Enter the total number of data records
reported (including the Code 1T) in the    data file.  Right justify
and zero fill. 
