<CENTER>
<CLEAR=LEFT><H2>Business Assistance Services</H2>
<BR><IMG SRC="/icon/line4.gif"></CENTER>
<P><h3>BUSINESS ASSISTANCE DIRECTORY</h3></P>
<P>The AQMD offers a wide array of services to help businesses comply with air quality rules, with a special emphasis on small businesses.  Free technical consultations, compliance training classes, and independent appeals process, and economic development office -- even loan guarantees to help businesses buy pollution control equipment.</P>
<P>The following offices at the AQMD offer specific services and assistance for businesses:</P>
<ul><li><a href = "baser.html#bc"><B>Billing and Customer Service</B></a> 
<li><a href = "baser.html#cc"><B>Compliance Course Information</B></a> 
<li><a href = "baser.html#ec"><B>Economic Development and Business Retention</B></a> 
<li><a href = "baser.html#fc"><B>Fee Review Committee</B></a>
<li><a href = "baser.html#gc"><B>Permit Application Information</B></a>
<li><a href = "baser.html#hc"><B>Public Advisor</B></a>
<li><a href = "http://www.aqmd.gov/prr/prrnet.html"><B>Public Records Requests</B></a>
<li><a href = "baser.html#ic"><B>Small Business Assistance</B></a>
<li><a href = "baser.html#jc"><B>Transportation (Rule 2202) Assistance</B></a>
<li><a href = "http://www.aqmd.gov/efb/efb.html"><B>1995-96 Annual Emission Reporting Program</B></a></ul>
<P>Other helpful information:</P>
<ul><li><a href = "/rules/rulesreg.html"><B>Rules and Regulations</B></a>
<li><a href = "/rules/proprules.html"><B>Proposed Rules</B></a>
<li><a href = "/pub_edu/pubedu1.html"><B>Public Workshops</B></a><B></ul>
