Items,<BR>
Pursuant to Government Code Section 54954.3)</B> 
<P>
There was no public comment on non-agenda items.
<P>
<U><B>ADJOURNMENT</B></U> 
<P>
The meeting was adjourned by Chairman Wedaa at 2:00 p.m.
<P>
The foregoing is a true statement of the proceedings held by the
South Coast Air Quality Management District Board on April 8,
1994.
