36.	Amend Regulation III - Fees	(Leyden)
(909) 396-3120 
 
Regulation III - Fees sets fee rates and schedules and is amended annually to support AQMD 
activities and operations, subject to a revenue cap imposed by SB 802 (Lewis).  Although 
