VOTE WAS CAST OF THE BOARD MEMBERS PRESENT (Absent: Lee, Loveridge,
Silva and Soto) APPROVING THE FOLLOWING APPOINTMENTS TO THE AQMD'S
HEARING BOARD, WITH TERMS ENDING JULY 1, 1998, AS RECOMMENDED:
<P>
