PC, LAN and WAN replacement parts and repair services. As a result
of successful responses to this RFP, three vendors were identified
as capable of providing these personal computer and telecommunications
repair services and supplies. These vendors will be the primary
source for all hard disk, printer, modem and other telecommunication
subsystem repairs and supplies. Staff recommends that these top
three vendors be approved and qualified to provide services and
supplies to the AQMD. Funds have been allocated in the FY 1995-96
Information Management Budget for these services. This recommendation
was reviewed and approved by the Administrative Committee on June
23, 1995.</I> 
