<B>22. <A HREF="950722.html">Recommendation to Implement the Home Rule Working Group </A>(Leyden)
</B>
<P>
<A HREF="mailto:pleyden@aqmd.gov"><IMG Align=Top SRC="/icon/mails.gif" ALT="Mail"></A>
( pleyden@aqmd.gov )
<P>
<I>A Home Rule Working Group would be established, in partnership
with the regulated community, to streamline regulatory compliance
and eliminate duplicative local, state and federal requirements.
This proposal will implement Item VI in the Board's Business Clean
Air Partnership. This recommendation was reviewed and approved
by the Stationary Source Committee on June 23, 1995.</I> 
