from qualified security companies to provide guard services at
the Diamond Bar Headquarters. This recommendation is to award
a three-year contract to the most qualified bidder for an amount
not to exceed $223,036 per year. Funding for this work has been
allocated in the FY 1995-96 budget. This recommendation was reviewed
and approved by the Administrative Committee on June 23, 1995.</I>

