1. Opening Comments
<P>
<U>James M. Lents, Ph.D., Executive Officer</U>. Announced that
a fuel cell bus co-sponsored by AQMD and the Department of Energy
was on display at AQMD Headquarters. The bus, which operates on
methanol and converts the methanol to hydrogen, will be operated
by the MTA.
