REQUIRED, IF EPA ADOPTS REVISIONS TO THE FEDERAL OPERATING PERMIT
PROGRAM (TITLE V), AND PRESENT IT BEFORE THE BOARD FOR CONSIDERATION
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE; AND
<P>
4) INCLUDE THAT, UPON COMPLETION OF ALL REVISIONS TO THE TGD,
IT SHALL BE USED FOR IMPLEMENTATION OF REGULATION XXX.
<P>
At Mr. Hewitt's suggestion,
<P>
