September 8, 1995
<P>
South Coast Air Quality
<H3><CENTER> Management District Board Administrative Committee
Report <FONT SIZE=5></H3>

<H3></FONT></H3>
<HR>

<P>
The Administrative Committee met on August 18, 1995, for its monthly
review of the upcoming Board agenda. In addition to a review of
the agenda, the Committee specifically approved staff recommendations
for the agenda items specified in Attachment &quot;A.&quot; The
Administrative Committee further held discussions on improving
customer service for incoming telephone calls to the District,
the position of Chief Prosecutor, and the investment of AQMD funds.
<P>
Attachment &quot;B&quot; is the Chairman's report on Board Member
travel authorized during the period July 21 to August 18, 1995.
<P>
The next Administrative Committee meeting is Friday, September
22, 1995, at
<P>
9:30 a.m.
<P>
THEREFORE IT IS RECOMMENDED THAT THE BOARD
<P>
--Receive and file this report.
<P>
Sincerely,
<P>
Jon D. Mikels
<P>
Chairman of the Board
<P>
Chairman of the Administrative Committee
<P>
