Attachments
<P>
(895bdl.doc)<HR>

<H4>ATTACHMENT II</H4>

<P>
<B>SOUTH COAST AIR QUALITY MANAGEMENT DISTRICT</B> 
<P>
<B>MOBILE SOURCE COMMITTEE</B> 
<P>
August 25, 1995
<P>
<B>ATTENDANCE SHEET</B><HR>

<P>
