( pleyden@aqmd.gov )
<P>
<I>At its August 11, 1995 meeting, the Board directed staff to
develop a voluntary pilot program. Under the program, AQMD will
prepare HRAs for facilities in the AB 2588 program. As a part
of the program's development, the AQMD will retain one or more
consultants through the standard competitive bidding process to
prepare the HRAs at a fixed cost. This item was reviewed and approved
by the Stationary Source Committee on August 18, 1995.</I> 
